----------------------|------------|-----------|---------------|-------------
Performance Only      | RAID 0     | 2         | None          | Excellent
Basic Redundancy      | RAID 1     | 2         | 50%           | Good Read
Balanced Performance  | RAID 5     | 3         | 1 disk        | Good
