<h3>Q: Should I use NFS or SMB for file sharing?<a class="headerlink" href="#q-should-i-use-nfs-or-smb-for-file-sharing" title="Link to this heading"></a></h3>
<p><strong>A:</strong> Choose based on your environment:</p>
