<section id="q-my-system-won-t-boot-after-storage-changes-how-do-i-fix-it">
<h3>Q: My system won’t boot after storage changes. How do I fix it?<a class="headerlink" href="#q-my-system-won-t-boot-after-storage-changes-how-do-i-fix-it" title="Link to this heading"></a></h3>
